threshold.description: Number of missed pings (3-64) before rebooting

srcalias.description: Name of IPv4 source network resource

dstalias.description: Name of IPv4 destination network resource

vlanid.description: VLAN ID of the transit interface for peer traffic

ipaddr.description: IP address of transit vlan in peer gateway
Starting IP address of peer uplink tunnel

sess_percent.description: Percentage of total supported sessions (by default equally distributed across all wired uplinks)

apn-name.description: Access Point Name (e.g. internet) - contact your service provider if unknown

isp-name.description: Internet Service Provider from supported ISP ( D-Telekom or Telekom)

APN-Profile-Pid.description: Connection id in modem dial string (e.g. '*99***x#', where 'x' is the appropriate APN-profile-id number in dial-string)

key.description: Key used to authenticate messages between systems. Length must be between 10 and 64 characters. Use 'no key' to revert to the default key.
